inish in the men's 100-meter final.\\u00c2World Athletics According to official race data, Noah Lyles had the worst reaction time of the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 100-meter final, as he was in last place for the first 40 meters and still in seventh at the halfway point.\", \"from\": 13842, \"to\": 14100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 13939, \"end\": 13949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The photo finish\", \"from\": 13842, \"to\": 13858}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meter final\", \"from\": 13862, \"to\": 13887}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2World Athletics\", \"from\": 13888, \"to\": 13904}, {\"ngram\": \"official race data\", \"from\": 13918, \"to\": 13936}, {\"ngram\": \"the worst reaction time\", \"from\": 13953, \"to\": 13976}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 100-meter final\", \"from\": 13980, \"to\": 14007}, {\"ngram\": \"last place\", \"from\": 14022, \"to\": 14032}, {\"ngram\": \"the first 40 meters\", \"from\": 14037, \"to\": 14056}, {\"ngram\": \"the halfway point\", \"from\": 14081, \"to\": 14098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, he never led the race until the final few steps, pipping by the smallest of margins Kishane Thompson, who was winning for much of the sprint, according to the data.\", \"from\": 14102, \"to\": 14275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14203, \"end\": 14211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.6353476951482194, \"rank\": 0.5739412685846718, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 14105, \"to\": 14109}, {\"n