to\": 14716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14565, \"end\": 14575, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reaction time\", \"from\": 14514, \"to\": 14527}, {\"ngram\": \"races.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 14541, \"to\": 14550}, {\"ngram\": \"Jamaica\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Kishane Thompson\\u00c2\", \"from\": 14591, \"to\": 14620}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter final\", \"from\": 14629, \"to\": 14648}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 14654, \"to\": 14662}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 14671, \"to\": 14679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI did think Thompson had it at the end,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Lyle told a scrum of reporters.\", \"from\": 14718, \"to\": 14795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14733, \"end\": 14741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.8934542543216109, \"rank\": 0.11924922612548998, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 14752, \"to\": 14759}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyle\", \"from\": 14764, \"to\": 14768}, {\"ngram\": \"a scrum\", \"from\": 14774, \"to\": 14781}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 14785, \"to\": 14794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI went up to him afterward, while we were waiting.\", \"from\": 14796, \"to\": 14849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 14796, \"to\": 14800}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I even said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Bro I think you got that one, big dog.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 And and then my name popped up and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Oh, my gosh, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m amazing!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he added with a laugh.\", \"from\": 14850, \"to\": 15014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big dog.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\", \"from\": 14896, \"to\": 14907}, {\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 14921, \"to\": 14928}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 14943, \"to\": 14948}, {\"ngram\": \"my gosh\", \"from\": 14962, \"to\": 14969}, {\"ngram\": \"a laugh\", \"from\": 15006, \"to\": 15013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When his name did show up on the giant screen in the stadium, Lyles said, it came as a rare surprise for a man never short of self-confidence.\", \"from\": 15016, \"to\": 15158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15078, \"end\": 15083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9849100585410381, \"rank\": 0.014819720780146909, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his name\", \"from\": 15021, \"to\": 15029}, {\"ngram\": \"the giant screen\", \"from\": 15045, \"to\": 15061}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 15065, \"to\": 15076}, {\"ngram\": \"a rare surprise\", \"from\": 15101, \"to\": 15116}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 15121, \"to\": 15126}, {\"ngram\": \"self-confidence\", \"from\": 15142, \"to\": 15157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to be honest, I wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t ready to see it,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said.\", \"from\": 15160, \"to\": 15228, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 15160, \"to\": 15168}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the first time I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve ever said that in my head that I wasn\\u00e2