h Ngamba won by unanimous decision, she grabbed a board and pointed to the Refugee Olympic Team name for the camera and the crowds.\", \"from\": 32344, \"to\": 32519, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32390, \"end\": 32396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\", \"score\": 0.999983636982345, \"rank\": 1.6313101065546514e-05, \"text\": \"Ngamba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ngambaa\"}, {\"begin\": 32463, \"end\": 32483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.598496311678609, \"rank\": 0.6708540723285282, \"text\": \"Refugee Olympic Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee_Olympic_Team_at_the_2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 32347, \"to\": 32354}, {\"ngram\": \"her fight\", \"from\": 32358, \"to\": 32367}, {\"ngram\": \"Michel\", \"from\": 32376, \"to\": 32382}, {\"ngram\": \"unanimous decision\", \"from\": 32404, \"to\": 32422}, {\"ngram\": \"a board\", \"from\": 32436, \"to\": 32443}, {\"ngram\": \"the camera\", \"from\": 32493, \"to\": 32503}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 32508, \"to\": 32518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After winning bronze in women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s uneven bars, Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Suni Lee told reporters thatafter a challenging time battling kidney disease, her main goal today was redemption.\", \"from\": 32521, \"to\": 32694, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32581, \"end\": 32589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Suni Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunisa_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 32535, \"to\": 32541}, {\"ngram\": \"uneven bars\", \"from\": 32555, \"to\": 32566}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters thatafter\", \"from\": 32595, \"to\": 32614}, {\"ngram\": \"kidney disease\", \"from\": 32643, \"to\": 32657}, {\"ngram\": \"her main goal\", \"from\": 32659, \"to\": 32672}, {\"ngram\": \"redemption\", \"from\": 32683, \"to\": 32693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI told myself that I was coming back to redeem myself on bars and that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what I did this time; I really wanted to just put a good, clean routine together,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Lee.\", \"from\": 32696, \"to\": 32868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32864, \"end\": 32867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.6118086296911688, \"rank\": 0.6339687251780718, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 32696, \"to\": 32700}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 32756, \"to\": 32760}, {\"ngram\": \"a good, clean routine\", \"from\": 32824, \"to\": 32845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI saw that I could if I just did the routine that I did the past couple of days, then I could have medaled.\", \"from\": 32869, \"to\": 32979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 32869, \"to\": 32873}, {\"ngram\": \"the routine\", \"from\": 32905, \"to\": 32916}, {\"ngram\": \"the past couple\", \"from\": 32928, \"to\": 32943}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 32947, \"to\": 32951}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wanted to go up there and prove to myself that I can do it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Some may think Lee had an advantage in going last because she knew what she needed to do.\", \"from\": 32980, \"to\": 33140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33066, \"end\": 33069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.6118086296911688, \"rank\": 0.6339687251780718, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 33043, \"to\": 33049}, {\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 33073, \"to\": 33085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But she said \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cit\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a lot harder because I had to watch everybody in front of me, so it definitely put the pressure on.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Lee\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s teammate Simone Bileswarned journalists earlier in the dayto \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cstop asking athletes what\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s next after they win a medal at the Olympics.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d When NBC News asked Lee whether she could return at Los Angeles 2028, she locked her stare, gave a half smile, waited a beat and said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cNo comment.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The race for a vault medal came down to tenths of a point, the equivalent of a foot shuffle upon landing.\", \"from\": 33141, \"to\": 33677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33423, \"end\": 33431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"score\": 0.9993227857285707, \"rank\": 0.0004996702181804873, \"text\": \"NBC News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_News\"}, {\"begin\": 33438, \"end\": 33441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9989895082101136, \"rank\": 0.0006527533011165169, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 33470, \"end\": 33486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\":