es \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 the men's 100-meters.\", \"from\": 52278, \"to\": 52492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 52326, \"end\": 52334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9966287654249882, \"rank\": 0.0033755386132584496, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 52389, \"end\": 52399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 gold medals\", \"from\": 52283, \"to\": 52297}, {\"ngram\": \"a big medal haul\", \"from\": 52357, \"to\": 52373}, {\"ngram\": \"the most eagerly-anticipated events\", \"from\": 52418, \"to\": 52453}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 52457, \"to\": 52466}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meters\", \"from\": 52471, \"to\": 52491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles has claimed throughout the build-up to the Olympics he is the fastest man on the planet after winning the world title last year, but with Jamaica's Kishane Thompson and Oblique Seville also in the mix, this looks set to be one of the most hyped and competitive 100-metre races since the days of Usain Bolt.\", \"from\": 52494, \"to\": 52806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 52638, \"end\": 52645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.999997165231928, \"rank\": 2.348575707973019e-06, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}, {\"begin\": 52656, \"end\": 52664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.7913005204741551, 